snippet.title: "Cutie Honey Flash" for Sega Pico (Part 1)
snippet.description:
Apparently someone in Japan wanted to educate kids about fanservice and being a pervert... this game otherwise has no educational value whatsoever - it is, however, potentially challenging with it's difficulty-level adjustment.

This game has some relatively strange story-cutscenes that interrupt the gameplay.
